{"tid":1792987,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又話罷搭黨鐵?點解新城今年會蝕1.6億","createTime":"2019-12-22T04:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T10:56:47.000Z","uid":29514,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ccc304a58ed1baa1cca238a1a0dba3366306e4d9","tid":1792987,"uid":29514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:53:54.000Z","msg":"立法會交通事務委員會今（20日）開會，討論新巴/城巴早前向政府提交的加價申請。新巴/城巴董事總經理鍾澤文透露，公司曾評估是否推出月票，不過最終認為推出月票後，收入損失會大過吸引到的額外客量，認為不值得推出。<br />\n<br />\n鍾澤文又稱，新巴/城巴曾跟其他巴士公司研究跨公司轉乘優惠，不過期間發現各自營運的路線，票價收入有差別，問題複雜難解決。至於會否重組路線，新巴/城巴指需交運輸署協調。<br />\n<br />\n被問到社會運動出期間，有市民聲稱罷坐港鐵，巴士客量卻未見上升，鍾澤文解釋，今年5月以後的月份，客量有升有跌，加上11月紅隧封閉對公司造成很大影響，提出加價申請時，無料過社會事件長時間持續下去。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">城巴和新巴於2018/19年度分別虧蝕8,883萬元和7,119萬元；相比2017/18年度的260萬元及510萬元，虧蝕大幅颷逾30倍及13倍</span>。而城巴及新巴繼今年初獲准加價後，8月再向運輸署申請加價12%，當局指若車費水平不變，虧損將持續惡化。<br />\n<br />\n真心覺得新城做得好過九巴, 自從開左南港島線之後就一直蝕到而家, 遲早步埋中巴後塵<br />\n大家又可以齊齊搭黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa36001f9f5a321b74fc0bf10785192db5c47c69","tid":1792987,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:55:07.000Z","msg":"港島好多巴士都好撚平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1d0fb50562df2c7d7c916e4150012f875aac6e","tid":1792987,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5zjT1qE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zjT1qE.jpg&h=f1f65c75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日三點半，麻煩大家準時！<br />\n現場唔好有連豬，連狗<br />\n尊重返人哋啲宗教<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TAHBZcu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTAHBZcu.gif&h=f5f36c0c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zpRGqSx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzpRGqSx.gif&h=bc12f105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外，&Ouml;zil畀人屌到屎眼爛都冇跪<br />\n我哋聽日都要支持佢<br />\n<br />\nStand with Uyghur(We ga）, Stand with &Ouml;zil（奧燒）"},{"pid":"99c0982c5014dbf62018da7202b76e4ba97c4a33","tid":1792987,"uid":95716,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:58:26.000Z","msg":"城巴路線實在收得太平 堅城去北角仲係$3.7<br />\n九巴最少要$7"},{"pid":"737e9087aa8243533130851843ef6294b493909a","tid":1792987,"uid":29514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fa36001f9f5a321b74fc0bf10785192db5c47c69","tid":1792987,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:55:07.000Z","msg":"港島好多巴士都好撚平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:58:31.000Z","msg":"所以今次加價真係無可厚非<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我寧願佢加價都好過執柒比黨鐵獨大"},{"pid":"c356079a3f5b0438336906ebc282bad1987959f1","tid":1792987,"uid":200714,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T05:02:30.000Z","msg":"不了 加價寧願5出街算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3a8c7330b3ac4877714f2dbf2680d1577c8510","tid":1792987,"uid":190333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T05:04:21.000Z","msg":"純官想賣盤"},{"pid":"ccf28fcf0a79a640344e11dac3fd83c3e0a4c1dd","t